mataroa.el
==========

`mataroa.el' is a (work-in-progress) Emacs package for interacting with blogs 
hosted within the `mataroa.blog' blogging platform via its API.

requirements
------------
Emacs 27.x+ (uses `iso8601' library), and `request' package from MELPA 
(https://melpa.org/#/request)

